prodNameC: 伊姆諾康塞斯特抗嗜中性球細胞質自體抗體測定系統
ingredientsDesc:
ANCA Substrate Slides: human neutrophils stabilized and fixed on the wells. 10 x 10 
ANCA Sample Diluent: 100ml
cANCA Positive Control: 1.0 ml of cANCA positive human control serum.
pANCA Postive Control: 1.0 ml of pANCA positive human control serum.
cANCA Titratable Control: 0.25 ml of liquid stable
cANCA positive human control serum. PANCA Titratable Control: 0.25 ml of liquid stable pANCA positive human control serum.
ANCA Negative Control: 1.0 ml of ANCA negative human control serum.
Flurescent Antibody Goat anti-human IgG conjugated to FITC.
PBS Buffer: Catalog number 1011. Phosphate-buffered saline powder (0.01 M, pH 7.4±0.2).
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區敬業一路１６０號７樓
efficacy: 利用間接螢光抗體測定法半定量測定人類血清中的抗嗜中性球細胞質自體抗體。
